VectorStorePort ..> ChunkId
RetrieverPort ..> QueryRequest
RetrieverPort ..> RetrievalResult
EvaluatorPort ..> EvaluationDataset
EvaluatorPort ..> EvaluationMetrics
DocumentRepositoryPort ..> SourceDocument
IndexVersionRegistryPort ..> IndexVersion
IndexVersionRegistryPort ..> IndexVersionStatus
EventBusPort ..> DomainEvent

' ── Use Cases depend on Ports (not Adapters) ────────────────────────
IngestSourceUseCase *-- ScraperPort
IngestSourceUseCase *-- FilterPipeline
IngestSourceUseCase *-- DocumentRepositoryPort
IngestSourceUseCase *-- IndexVersionRegistryPort
IngestSourceUseCase *-- EventBusPort
IngestSourceUseCase *-- ErrorHandlerPort
IngestSourceUseCase *-- ProgressReporterPort
